OL,3,CMiners march on Downing Street against
OL,4,C'daylight robbery' in pension row
OL,6,FFormer miners have marched on Downing
OL,7,FStreet calling on the government to
OL,8,Freturn money to a pension scheme which
OL,9,Fthey say could benefit some of the
OL,10,Fpoorest communities in the country.
OL,12,FAround 50 ex-pit workers from the
OL,13,FNorth East joined the protest in
OL,14,Fcentral London on Wednesday 8 May
OL,15,Fagainst what they call "the biggest
OL,16,Fpension grab of all time".
