OL,3,CMiners march on Downing Street against
OL,4,C'daylight robbery' in pension row
OL,6,F"We put the money in, British Coal put
OL,7,Fthe money in. British Coal had a
OL,8,Fholiday from the end of the miner's
OL,9,Fstrike till they closed. It's our
OL,10,Fmoney, it's not theirs.
OL,12,F"We hope to make that difference. This
OL,13,Fis only one rally. If we've got to
OL,14,Fkeep coming back to the day we stop
OL,15,Fbreathing, we'll be back."
