OL,3,CMiners march on Downing Street against
OL,4,C'daylight robbery' in pension row
OL,6,F"I think the miners have got a just
OL,7,Fdemand here and if this government
OL,8,Fwon't address it, I want to try and
OL,9,Fget a commitment that the next
OL,10,Fgovernment will."
OL,12,FIn response to the march, a Department
OL,13,Ffor Energy Security and Net Zero
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "We are protecting
OL,15,Fthe pensions of mineworkers, while
OL,16,Fstriking a fair balance between scheme
OL,17,Fmembers and taxpayers.
