OL,6,F"Mineworkers' Pension Scheme members
OL,7,Fare receiving payments 33 per cent
OL,8,Fhigher than they would have been as a
OL,9,Fresult of the Government's guarantee.
OL,11,F"On most occasions, the scheme has
OL,12,Fbeen in surplus, and scheme members
OL,13,Fhave received bonuses in addition to
OL,14,Ftheir guaranteed pension."
